<plot>Amedeo, a bestseller writer unable to write a new book, wanders in the small town of Matera looking for inspiration. Pasquale, a presenter of the local TV station, is fired and wanders in the town looking for a new job. Pasquale and Amedeo meet on a bench of a park every day. Their town has been changed by the movies industry, but even if they'll do everything to make their situations change, everything stays always the same.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339907</url></doc>
